<typeStatus box="[569,667,1699,1725]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">holotype</typeStatus>
was donated by Patrick Müller and is deposited in the author’s collection.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,259,1906]" box="[199,1058,1771,1798]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,370,1771,1797]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Syninclusions.</emphasis>
Remnants of insect legs, plant detritus and stellate plant hair.
</paragraph>
